<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.219232>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1 – 7. Gamasiphis ochotensis sp. n. Female. 1. Antiaxial view of chelicera; 2. Epistome: A – B variations of shape; B—epistome and salivary; 3. Hypostome; 4. Palp trochanter; 5. Dorsal view of idiosoma; 6. Ventral view of idiosoma; 7. Spermatheca." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/219232/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.219233>
    dc:description "FIGURES 8 – 12. Gamasiphis ochotensis sp. n. Male. 8. Chelicera: A – C variations of spermatodactyl shape, A, B—antiaxial view, C—paraxial view; 9. Corniculi; 10. Ventral view of idiosoma; 11. Leg II; 12. Spur-like setae of femur II." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/219233/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

